flowchart TD
  Start[User arrives] --> Choice{How do they think?}
  Choice --> Profile[Profile first]
  Choice --> Compare[Compare first]
  Choice --> Country[Country first]
  Choice --> PlanB[Plan B builder]

  Profile --> Q[8-12 local-only questions]
  Q --> Results[Likely / possible / blocked / needs review]
  Results --> Reasons[Cited reasons + missing info]
  Reasons --> Shortlist[Exportable shortlist]

  Compare --> Category[Pick category]
  Category --> Table[Side-by-side table]
  Table --> Shortlist

  Country --> Pages[Country + program pages]
  Pages --> Sources[Official sources + freshness]

  PlanB --> Timeline[3 months / 1 year / 3 years / 5 years]
  Timeline --> Buckets[Immediate stay / medium residence / long-term PR or citizenship]
  Buckets --> Shortlist
